bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2959640/extras/f15b16bf51a187a49b0b54e87785127e.avif?t=1762824617\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >—After being petrified, the head, torso, and feet were destroyed in turn,<br>she turned into dust and died. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2959640/extras/990f9299cac9910e7696081693edb427.avif?t=1762824617\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >—She was caught from behind by a large monster. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eventually both arms were torn off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A rich plot of more than 50,000 words. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The heroine has full Japanese dubbing. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 exquisite event CG pictures and 7 memory events. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Character】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2959640/extras/2392840b72e23975a11f98b5245cec01.avif?t=1762824617\" width=600 height=300 /></span>Colt (CV: 秋山はるる)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cheerful and smart elf girl with excellent archery skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She embarked on a journey to heal her sister.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2959640/extras/02fd1b2cb236eb9c53af19db41547b36.avif?t=1762824617\" width=600 height=300 /></span>Philum (CV: ゆづきひな。)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colt's sister, a girl who was born frail and sickly.</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2